Jimmy Jewel https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jimmy_Jewel 0 For the football manager see: Jimmy Jewell For the British climber see: Jimmy Jewell (climber)James Arthur Thomas Jewel Marsh (4 December 1909 – 3 December 1995), known professionally as Jimmy Jewel, was an English comedian and actor who enjoyed a long career in stage, radio, television and film productions, including a 32-year partnership with his cousin Ben Warriss.
